plot: With Negative 10 after the Sub-energy, the Tennysons and Cooper make a final stand at Mount Rushmore to keep them from getting it and taking over the world.

With Cooper's help, the Tennysons protect the Plumber base beneath Mt. Rushmore as members of Negative 10 lay siege. Voice analysis confirms Grandpa Max's suspicion that the Forever King is Driscoll, a former Plumber who years ago was kicked out in disgrace.—statmanjeff
